summary: Completed comprehensive testing of multi-tenant observability features (Milestone 0-1). All new features working correctly including health endpoints, JWT claims with org_id, org isolation, admin analytics access, and frontend regression tests.
passed_tests: Health endpoints: GET /api/health/live returns 200 {status:live}
Health endpoints: GET /api/health/ready returns 200 {status:ready} with DB and model checks
JWT tokens contain org_id and is_super_admin claims correctly
Admin JWT: org_id='ORG-CLINOMIC', is_super_admin=true
Lab JWT: org_id='ORG-LAB-2024-001', is_super_admin=false
Org isolation: Lab user can create screening under LAB-2024-001
Org isolation: Lab user sees only their own analytics data (2 cases)
Admin can access all analytics endpoints (/summary, /labs, /doctors, /cases)
Admin lab mapping: Admin can create screening with labId that maps to correct orgId
Frontend regression: Login page loads with demo credentials
Frontend regression: Lab user login and workspace access
Frontend regression: Admin login and dashboard access
Frontend regression: Logout functionality
Frontend regression: Navigation and UI interactions
Admin dashboard shows comprehensive analytics (14 total screenings, 92% model accuracy)
Case database shows multi-tenant data correctly
Mocked API /api/lis/parse-pdf still functional
All authentication and authorization flows preserved
Backend API latency optimal (45ms shown in dashboard)
Timing middleware working (X-Request-Id and X-Response-Time-Ms headers)
success_percentage: Backend: 100% (25/25 tests passed), Frontend: 100% (all UI flows working)
